                <h1 class="domdom">24</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/777">Naked Gun: From The Files Of Police Squad + Special Party Until 2am! (1988)</a></h1>

                <h2>24 Apr 2011, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>One of the funniest comedies ever made! ZAZ-team's (Zucker-Abrahams-Abrahams) fast-paced slapstick comedy is full of visual and verbal puns and gags masterfully delivered by the late Leslie Nielsen as the Lieutenant Frank Drebin from Police Squad!
</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/777">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

