                </div>

                <h1 class="domdom">28</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/778">Top Secret! + Spy Fancy Dress Party + Djs Until 12pm! (1984)</a></h1>

                <h2>28 Apr 2011, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>One of the greatest comedies of our time! The film is a parody of the GDR era and Elvis films in which young Val Kilmer does his second best in his first ever feature role! This joyful insanity is once again brought to you by the great Zucker-Abrahams-Zucker's ZAZ-team!</p>

