                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/781">Airplane! (1980)</a></h1>

                <h2>15 May 2011, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>The second funniest film ever made! The crown jewel of team Zucker-Abrahams-Zucker's ZAZ-comedies takes you to the wildest flight ever made! The writing, delivery, Leslie Nielsen, Lloyd Bridges and overall surreal craziness just takes over; A true work of genius! This Cpt. Oveur Over. </p>

